Sentencas: The electrical properties of doped SrCeO(3) and BaCeO(3) were studied as a function of temperature, and oxygen and water vapor partial pressure using electrochemical impedance spectroscopy.
Titulo: Mixed Protonic/Electronic Conductor Cathodes for Intermediate Temperature SOFCs Based on Proton Conducting Electrolytes

Sentencas: Rare-earth elements, such as Yb, Eu, and Sm, were used as cation dopants because of their multivalent oxidation state, low third ionization potential, and comparable ionic radius with cerium.
Titulo: Mixed Protonic/Electronic Conductor Cathodes for Intermediate Temperature SOFCs Based on Proton Conducting Electrolytes

Sentencas: Higher conductivity values were recorded doping SrCeO(3) and BaCeO(3) oxides with Yb.
Titulo: Mixed Protonic/Electronic Conductor Cathodes for Intermediate Temperature SOFCs Based on Proton Conducting Electrolytes

Sentencas: Partial conductivities and transport numbers were calculated from the conductivity measurements at different oxygen partial pressures using an established defect model.
Titulo: Mixed Protonic/Electronic Conductor Cathodes for Intermediate Temperature SOFCs Based on Proton Conducting Electrolytes

Sentencas: In an oxidizing condition, electron-hole conduction was dominant at high temperatures and decreased with decreasing the temperature and increasing the water vapor content in the gas atmosphere.
Titulo: Mixed Protonic/Electronic Conductor Cathodes for Intermediate Temperature SOFCs Based on Proton Conducting Electrolytes

Sentencas: BaCe(0.9)Yb(0.1)O(3-delta) presented the highest conductivity among the tested samples both in dry and wet oxygen atmospheres.
Titulo: Mixed Protonic/Electronic Conductor Cathodes for Intermediate Temperature SOFCs Based on Proton Conducting Electrolytes

Sentencas: Moreover, BaCe(0.9)Yb(0.1)O(3-delta) showed a mixed conduction of ions and holes at temperatures above 600 degrees C, suggesting that this perovskite-type oxide could be a possible cathode material in a solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) based on a proton conductor electrolyte.
Titulo: Mixed Protonic/Electronic Conductor Cathodes for Intermediate Temperature SOFCs Based on Proton Conducting Electrolytes
